tafsir[4]{c,v,t}:
  44,1,"Ḥā Mīm. The discussion on similar letters has already passed in Sūrah Al-Baqarah."
  44,2,"Allah takes an oath on the Qur’ān which clearly explains the path of guidance towards the truth."
  44,8,"There is no true deity except him. He gives life and causes death; there is no one that does that except Him. He is your Lord and the Lord of your forefathers before you."
  44,10,"So O Messenger! Wait for their punishment that will come soon: a day when the sky is clearly filled with smoke."